  "link": "https:\/\/murphlaw.net\/about-us\/",
  "title": { "rendered": "Our Vision" },
  "content": {
    "rendered": "<div class=\"wpb-content-wrapper\"><p>[vc_row triangle_shape=&#8221;no&#8221;][vc_column][vc_empty_space height=&#8221;20px&#8221;][vc_row_inner content_width=&#8221;grid&#8221;][vc_column_inner width=&#8221;1\/2&#8243;][vc_column_text]<\/p>\n<h3><strong>OUR PRACTICE<\/strong><\/h3>\n<p>Chuckstern Murphy Law Firm is a specialized boutique law firm located in the heart of Fresno, CA. Our firm is equipped with aggressive trial lawyers who have been collectively practicing for over 50 years.<\/p>\n<p>The best way to describe us is by having GRIT:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>goal-oriented<\/li>\n<li>resilient<\/li>\n<li>intuitive<\/li>\n<li>trustworthy<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>We represent all types of clients and we will give you the time and respect that you deserve. We handle all of our legal matters with the utmost integrity, honesty, compassion, professionalism, and personal attention to detail.[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=&#8221;1\/2&#8243;][vc_single_image image=&#8221;8376&#8243; img_size=&#8221;full&#8221;][\/vc_column_inner][\/vc_row_inner][vc_empty_space height=&#8221;60&#8243;][\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row content_width=&#8221;grid&#8221; triangle_shape=&#8221;no&#8221;][vc_column width=&#8221;1\/2&#8243;][vc_single_image image=&#8221;8382&#8243; img_size=&#8221;full&#8221;][\/vc_column][vc_column width=&#8221;1\/2&#8243;][vc_column_text]Our specialty areas include business\/corporate law, contract drafting and negotiations, unfair business practices, personal injury, wrongful death, wills &amp; trusts, real estate matters, landlord-tenant issues, employment law, business fraud, debt collection, and intellectual property matters. Our firm is dynamic and creative in finding legal solutions for all of our clients while navigating through the complexities of the legal system.<\/p>\n<p>In addition to serving our clients, we sincerely believe in the importance of serving our local communities through donations, volunteer work, forming and assisting non-profits, providing free legal aid and advice to those in need, and building community networks. Our firm strongly believes in the need to give back to our communities.<\/p>\n<p>Chuckstern Murphy Law Firm has served clients in  Fresno County, Fresno County, Orange County, San Diego County, Santa Barbara County, San Francisco County, and out-of-state. We would be more than happy to talk to you about any legal questions you may have and assist you in finding the best solution. Please contact us today to schedule an appointment. We look forward to meeting you.[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row triangle_shape=&#8221;no&#8221;][vc_column][vc_empty_space height=&#8221;60&#8243;][\/vc_column][\/vc_row]<\/p>\n<\/div>",
    "protected": false
  },
  "excerpt": {
    "rendered": "<p>[vc_row triangle_shape=&#8221;no&#8221;][vc_column][vc_empty_space height=&#8221;20px&#8221;][vc_row_inner content_width=&#8221;grid&#8221;][vc_column_inner width=&#8221;1\/2&#8243;][vc_column_text] OUR PRACTICE Chuckstern Murphy Law Firm is a specialized boutique law firm located in the heart of Fresno, CA. Our firm is equipped with aggressive trial lawyers who have been collectively practicing for over 50 years. The best way to describe us is by having GRIT: goal-oriented resilient intuitive trustworthy We represent all types of clients and we will give you the time and respect that you deserve. We handle all of our legal matters with the utmost integrity, honesty, compassion, professionalism, and personal attention to detail.[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=&#8221;1\/2&#8243;][vc_single_image image=&#8221;8376&#8243; img_size=&#8221;full&#8221;][\/vc_column_inner][\/vc_row_inner][vc_empty_space height=&#8221;60&#8243;][\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row&#8230;<\/p>\n",
